Solutions

Adledge helps you achieve Safer and More Visible Ad Campaign

Fraud

   Our offer, which combines visibility and brand safety, makes it
   possible to detect fraud within the visibility of the ads, as well as
   fraud on display conditions.

Viewability

   Adledge visibility allows you to know which part of the area of your ad
   was viewed, for how many seconds and from what part of the world it was
   seen.

Brand safety

   Adledge identifies damaging context for your ads and allows you to
   verify that your brand is safe and to improve your campaigns.
